enjoyProducts.description:
CANCELLATION PROTECTION

If you pay in full online for your rental, you will normally have FREE cancellation, meaning you can cancel your booking and receive a full refund up to 48 hours prior to the start of your rental. You must have a valid credit card (or payment method accepted by the Supplier) with you, and it must be in the same name as the named driver on the Rental Agreement. If you do not have this, the Supplier may insist that you purchase additional insurance or may refuse the Vehicle.
